question.title: java.lang.NoSuchFieldError: Class org.springframework.util.SystemPropertyUtils does not have member field 'java.lang.Character ESCAPE_CHARACTER'
question.body:

    12:54:11.255 [main] ERROR org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication -- Application run failed

    at org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication.run(SpringApplication.java:313)

Disconnected from the target VM, address: '127.0.0.1:56343', transport: 'socket'

Spring is attempting to access a field ESCAPE_CHARACTER in the SystemPropertyUtils class. But this field does not exist.

As I understood there is mismatch between versions of spring libraries, but I cant figure out between which ones exactly. Here is my POM.
